OL,3,CMan jailed for taking 'silly' pictures
OL,4,Cduring court case over boy's death
OL,6,FA man has been jailed for taking
OL,7,Fphotos in court and posting them on
OL,8,Fsocial media with "silly captions".
OL,10,FKane Thompson took the pictures at
OL,11,FNewcastle Crown Court on Monday, where
OL,12,Fhis brother was in the dock accused of
OL,13,Fviolent disorder in connection to the
OL,14,Fdeath of 14-year-old Gordon Gault.
OL,16,FThompson, 24, of no fixed abode,
OL,17,Fposted the images on Facebook and
OL,18,FInstagram with emojis and "silly
OL,19,Fcaptions".
