OL,3,CMan jailed for taking 'silly' pictures
OL,4,Cduring court case over boy's death
OL,6,FHe pleaded guilty to two charges of
OL,7,Fcontempt of court and was jailed for
OL,8,Fsix months.
OL,10,FJudge Edward Bindloss said he became
OL,11,Faware that photographs taken in the
OL,12,Fcourtroom which showed three of the
OL,13,Fdefendants, including Liam Thompson
OL,14,Fand Jack Hardy in the dock, along with
OL,15,Fa dock officer.
OL,17,FThe judge arranged for Thompson to be
OL,18,Farrested on Tuesday and an
OL,19,Finvestigation was carried out
OL,20,Fovernight.
