OL,4,Cduring court case over boy's death
OL,6,F"The photos are no longer on your
OL,7,FInstagram or Facebook to view, but any
OL,8,Fscreenshotted copies could still be
OL,9,Fdistributed to numbers unknown. It's
OL,10,Fnot known how far they have been
OL,11,Fdisseminated."
OL,13,FThe judge added that court dock
OL,14,Fofficers are entitled to anonymity
OL,15,Fwhile at work, but the pictures
OL,16,FThompson posted clearly showed the
OL,17,Fface of one.
