OL,6,FIn mitigation, Mairi Clancy, explained
OL,7,Fthat the images had been posted to
OL,8,FThompson's Instagram stories so would
OL,9,Fhave only been visible for 24 hours,
OL,10,Fand he deleted them when he realised
OL,11,Fwhat he had done wrong.
OL,13,FWant a quick and expert briefing on
OL,14,Fthe biggest news stories? Listen to
OL,15,Four latest podcasts to find out What
OL,16,FYou Need To Know...
OL,18,FShe added his actions were the result
OL,19,Fof "stupidity" and he had not intended
OL,20,Fto cause harm.
