OL,6,FShe said: "His position is he panicked
OL,7,Fon realising the seriousness of what
OL,8,Fhe had done.
OL,10,F"This was an extremely stupid and
OL,11,Fidiotic thing for him to do, but
OL,12,Fnothing more sinister than stupidity
OL,13,Fand naivety.
