OL,3,CMan jailed for taking 'silly' pictures
OL,4,Cduring court case over boy's death
OL,6,F"The focus of the photos are his
OL,7,Fbrother in the dock. They were light-
OL,8,Fhearted. He's posted some quite silly
OL,9,Fcaptions and an emoji with sunglasses."
OL,11,FThompson was in court for the start of
OL,12,Fa trial involving six people accused
OL,13,Fof violent disorder, including his
OL,14,Fbrother Liam Thompson, 28.
OL,16,FThe six all pleaded guilty to affray
OL,17,Fover escalating violence in Newcastle,
OL,18,Fwhich resulted in the death of Gordon
OL,19,Fin November 2022. He was stabbed in
OL,20,Fthe arm during an incident in Elswick
OL,21,Fand died in hospital six days later.
