OL,6,FJack Hardy and Raymond Matthew, who
OL,7,Fare both 18, and Liam Thompson will be
OL,8,Fsentenced at a later date, along with
OL,9,Fthree 17-year-old boys, who cannot be
OL,10,Fnamed for legal reasons.
OL,12,FLast month Carlos Neto, 18, of
OL,13,FSalford, and Lawson Natty, 18, of
OL,14,FNewbiggin Hall, who denied murdering
OL,15,FGordon, were convicted of manslaughter
OL,16,Ffollowing a trial at Newcastle Crown
OL,17,FCourt.
